Enjoy @Chubby Snacks Strawberry Sandwich{6%unit} and @Chubby Snacks Grape Sandwich{6%unit}.

Add @Chubby Snacks Almond Butter Strawberry Sandwich{2%unit} and @Chubby Snacks Almond Butter Grape Sandwich{2%unit}.

Include @Chubby Snacks Sunflower Butter Strawberry Sandwich{2%unit} and @Chubby Snacks Sunflower Butter Grape Sandwich{2%unit}.

> Peanut butter and jelly is one of the most lovable combos out there, which is why
> Chubby Snacks made a better-for-you snack to deliver on those nostalgic flavors.
> Made with superfood jams, creamy nut butters, and whole-grain bread, these
> pre-packaged frozen sandwiches are high in protein and fiber with no added sugar.
> One order contains the following sammies: Peanut Butter & Strawberry Jam,
> Peanut Butter & Grape Jam, Almond Butter & Strawberry Jam, Almond Butter & Grape Jam,
> Sunflower Butter & Strawberry Jam, and Sunflower Butter & Grape Jam. Enjoy them ice
> cold from the freezer or warm them up in the toaster!